abstract: >-
  Parse, de-identify, structure, and export radiology free-text reports to
  FHIR. Rule-based, zero-dependency extraction of sections, measurements,
  critical findings, and follow-up recommendations, plus PHI redaction for
  research and analytics pipelines.
keywords:
  - radiology
  - FHIR
  - medical imaging
  - healthcare
  - NLP
  - de-identification
  - PHI
  - structured reporting
